metadata.name: White Shirt
metadata.description:
She's subtle. She's chic. She's classy.

Ispired by timeless fashion, the 1/1 'White shirt' is a digitally hand drawn piece in Procreate. A  celebration classic fashion illustration and great style.

This NFT is also a reminder of bridging the gap between classic art of fashion and drawing and taking it into the new era. 

Celebrating women in style.
